item.title: Another Start
item.description: Hey We are now one week into 2021. Among all the festivities, celebrations, and general newness in my life, I’m reminded to take some time to write down my intentions. This follows what has been a notable year to most, including myself. In Retrospect Looking back, 2020 did not live up to my expectations (no great surprise there,) though it was not all bad. I would qualify this past year as passive, if I were to choose a single word for it.
